quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Ɗuum ko sabu woowde Quraysi en."
  106,2,"Goowgol mu'en ɗatngal dabbunde e ceeɗu."
  106,3,"Yoo ɓe ndew jom ndu suudu."
  106,4,"Oon ñamminɗo ɓe saanga heege e hoolni ɓe e kulol."
  107,1,"Mbele a anndii oon jeddoowo njoɓdi ñande daranga"
  107,2,"E Ko oon duñoowo alyatiime."
  107,3,"O reerɗintaa e ñammiingol miskiina(wa'asɓe)."
  107,4,"Halkaare woodanii juulooɓe ɓeen."
  107,5,"Ɓeen welsandiiɓe ndeer juulde maɓɓe."
  107,6,"Ɓeen yi'inatooɓe."
  107,7,"Heɓe kaɗa ngenndukoñ."
  108,1,"Min tottiima(weendu )alKawsara."
  108,2,"juulan joom ma mboroɗa."
  108,3,"Tigi ko gañɗo ma o woni taƴiiɗo."